{"tid":927248,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本最後「Call機」服務宣布明年終止服務","createTime":"2018-12-04T04:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T05:53:16.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f708c5a8fa3f0966fce8c7e425baf5ecceba4f","tid":927248,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181204/_2018120410424978702.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181204%2F_2018120410424978702.jpg&h=cd9e50bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「嗶嗶嗶嗶......」、「係時候覆call喇」、「打上call台留言」、「借個電話覆call」，還記得這些傳呼機的用語嗎？「Call機」風行於90年代，是當時重要的無綫電通訊工具，不過在手機面世後，漸漸被取代。日本最後一家傳呼服務公司Tokyo Telemessage終究敵不過時代變遷，宣布明年9月將結束Call機服務，代表在日本有50年歷史的Call台服務也將成為「集體回憶」。<br />\n<br />\n據日媒報導，日本電信公司 Tokyo Telemessage是目前全日本僅存的呼叫器服務供應商，在當地一都三縣包括東京都、崎玉縣、神奈縣和千葉縣地區，仍有約1,500 名用戶使用服務。Tokyo Telemessage昨日宣布，2019年9月30日將全面終止個人傳呼服務，未來會集中資源發展防災用呼叫器產品，繼續為日本地方政府提供相關解決方案。<br />\n<br />\nTokyo Telemessage社長清野英俊表示，今後將活用傳呼台的無綫電波，把重心轉移到地方自治體為主的防災無綫事業，希望在日本的防災體系發揮作用。<br />\n<br />\n傳呼服務在日本被稱為「Pocket Bell」，報導指出，日本最早「Pocket Bell」由日本電信電話公社（NTT）推出，「Pocket Bell」見證了平成年代的通訊方式，包括公司和政府機構、醫院工作人員都曾廣泛使用，許多男孩也用來追高中女同學，因為初期的傳呼機只能靠傳送數字來表達訊息，而誕生許多諧音的數字暗碼，像是華人社會流行的「5201314」（我愛你一生一世）等，深受年輕族群的喜愛，直到現在這些都還被廣泛使用，現在手機出現後，用戶逐年減少，Call機已成為集體回憶。<br />\n<br />\n日本各大電信業者早已終止這項服務，日本電信龍頭NTT docomo也在2007年退出市場，現只剩下Tokyo Telemessage一家服務公司，在關東地區提供約不到1500名用戶服務。該社在2013年已經停止了新用戶的使用申請，並決定在明年9月結束服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/879598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F879598&d=c2Oj08GKES16mIsH3YW0ttZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=beb336bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F879598&h=cc53d94e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/879598</a>"},{"pid":"e0fca1814f986d7663cad6e0babb8a0a42ec17d0","tid":927248,"uid":193251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:51:09.000Z","msg":"時代的眼淚"},{"pid":"20ee61ad2dc9976d1515ef44689b7b08b7093bb6","tid":927248,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"時代的終結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f07b19dada9ff0f18be895a6e640008e471c19","tid":927248,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e47e7dfb905c4105ff813f79c047363b6c7d0f3","tid":927248,"uid":6044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:56:40.000Z","msg":"以前有本野係對番數字解暗號<br />\n太細個唔太記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b676b133315e20406f3839c98db3cd7f9528d2","tid":927248,"uid":189243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:58:17.000Z","msg":"&quot;攞袋 receipt 簿&quot;變&quot;攞袋護舒寶&quot;嘅笑話成為絕響"},{"pid":"9eb28fe2919996012f7f40f53542df0d8ce55dde","tid":927248,"uid":36544,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"5e47e7dfb905c4105ff813f79c047363b6c7d0f3","tid":927248,"uid":6044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:56:40.000Z","msg":"以前有本野係對番數字解暗號<br />\n太細個唔太記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NqX7pDF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNqX7pDF.jpg&h=191ddd3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"496e87e348e7cfa8ca79f0a387167bed59d698ec","tid":927248,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T05:49:15.000Z","msg":"今時今日先執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193d07f41bd25a9049ca541a17ca8f589663b39e","tid":927248,"uid":122570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"